fex2
0000 first line is the size of the stack
0004 second line is the size of the heap
0010 third line is the size of the code
# program code is located at <stack-size> + <heap-size>
 
0000 0010
0001 0000
0002 0000
0003 0000

# the code starts here
0004 m1.. load value to R[1] from memory address
0005 0000 (this address)
0006 d1.. display value in R[1]
0007 Z... display newline
0008 r1.. decrement R[1]
0009 01.. branch if R[1] is 0
0010 0013 (this is branch address)
0011 b... unconditional branch
0012 0006 (this is branch address)
0013 e... TERMINATE PROCESS
